{"tid":954700,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU對粉絲「愛屌你」 卯起來講中文","createTime":"2018-12-24T19:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-25T00:03:57.000Z","uid":34643,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94de97a6993d614bb185d6d44c840afb3db3cd44","tid":954700,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/2aaae3eed27825a0677077df0de7b148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2F2aaae3eed27825a0677077df0de7b148&h=8d1154a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國「國民妹妹」IU今（24日）平安夜在台北南港展覽館開唱，5,000個座位座無虛席，IU演唱會以影片開場，即讓現場粉絲不停揮舞手燈尖叫，她以耳熟能詳的〈The Red Shoes〉連歌帶舞立刻將氣氛炒得火熱，歌舞劇般的舞台加上舞群，IU甜美的嗓音融化了粉絲的心。</strong><br />\n<br />\n一連唱完〈The Red Shoes〉、〈Cruel Fairy Tale〉兩首歌曲，IU從黑色晚禮服換成亮麗的孔雀藍小禮服，IU以中文向粉絲問候：「大家好，我是IU，我很想念你們，今天晚上我會讓你們很幸福的。」時值平安夜，IU感謝粉絲將特別的日子在這裡與她一起度過。為了符合節慶氣氛，IU說自己特地打扮得比平常閃亮，連合音也戴著耶誕帽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/bc1ed751373e2e8bd9d6eeb9a950eee8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fbc1ed751373e2e8bd9d6eeb9a950eee8&h=c6e02ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU與舞群的表演讓人好像在看歌舞劇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/c035d5df06e32df95a4fea8badf16a4c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fc035d5df06e32df95a4fea8badf16a4c&h=56d0cfdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU與女舞群一起秀長腿，小露性感。<br />\n<br />\n前年IU在台灣第一次演唱會上唱了莫文蔚的〈愛情〉，讓粉絲非常驚艷，她說因為大家太喜歡，「好像每次來台灣一定要唱這首。」標準的台語發音與中文咬字，IU獨特的唱腔成功地將這首歌唱出自己的味道，唱完後不忘問粉絲喜歡嗎，「<span style=\"color: red;\">你們愛我嗎，我也是『愛丟哩』</span>（台語：愛上你）」。IU不時跟著翻譯莎莎的話講著中文，「真的好可愛啊」「可愛啊你們」，對粉絲的應援更是喜愛，「我很幸福，我愛你們」，讓粉絲不時尖叫給予回應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/fc4988d78ddb796d51c35b9f829be1bd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Ffc4988d78ddb796d51c35b9f829be1bd&h=7599edb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU說為了耶誕節，她和舞群都打扮得閃亮亮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/mirrormedia.mg/e621311aa7a86f30fb647d462cd98383\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2Fe621311aa7a86f30fb647d462cd98383&h=74740f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU稱讚粉絲都有她的手燈，「我記得周邊沒有在海外販售，怎麼大家都有呢？」<br />\n<br />\nIU這次來台灣，除了第一天走遍華山、士林夜市，大吃光華車輪餅，昨結束媒體見面會後，繼續觀光客模式，逛了台北101，吃鼎泰豐，還買了香水。今（24日）中午她與工作人員直接從飯店走到旁邊天吉屋用餐，對她的藝人身份毫不在意，這幾天不時被捕獲「野生IU」，她都很親切跟粉絲打招呼，平易近人的形象搏得超好感。IU明天在南港展覽館還有一場演出。"},{"pid":"835e37e6c89d324af39732182a4a149dd267565f","tid":954700,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:28:29.000Z","msg":"* &gt; <span style=\"color: red;\">米</span>"},{"pid":"d8179b26bc2b92229e56291840e5b12fa0b8547b","tid":954700,"uid":107364,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e55adca85f72492bbf509de2cdeffec01b15a485","tid":954700,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":30,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:33:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a13ccb538c7bd08688c5c6e4c3a1df6d68d83b5f","tid":954700,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"quote":{"pid":"d8179b26bc2b92229e56291840e5b12fa0b8547b","tid":954700,"uid":107364,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:31:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:37:32.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"9b13d8385ec000a47ddbac0ff8ce4010a6493f73","tid":954700,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:37:44.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"fc173017c722e6476e1fd3ec26bf1a811a79ba02","tid":954700,"uid":64374,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b84162cab1de4dc07879da39a6a05243b97962dd","tid":954700,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"fc173017c722e6476e1fd3ec26bf1a811a79ba02","tid":954700,"uid":64374,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T19:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536e436d669dec895e4abc4cd0affede640a9048","tid":954700,"uid":46435,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T20:04:42.000Z","msg":"IU世界第一"},{"pid":"f77ab46bf120e067f3f499a58ba0658acbaf82d9","tid":954700,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T21:05:23.000Z","msg":"樓主0負皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:我正皮左"},{"pid":"e2aa44b7199601d6f74805385dc5f91316faae64","tid":954700,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f77ab46bf120e067f3f499a58ba0658acbaf82d9","tid":954700,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T21:05:23.000Z","msg":"樓主0負皮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:我正皮左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:11:51.000Z","msg":"唔關我事, 只係iu太屈機"},{"pid":"f0be17fec122ab999f8a7e8ac2ee209257060850","tid":954700,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T23:29:09.000Z","msg":"我日日同佢講 搞到佢都跟住講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d882f2cc90c262290d43ea30fcb84ab7bf17719f","tid":954700,"uid":108596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T00:03:57.000Z","msg":"nanb呢"}]}